.h files
    Lua applications as strings.

linux_app.cc
    A linux application to test lua applications.
    
makefile_linux
    The makefile for linux_app.cc


In order to compile Lua applications for EPOS, set the variable APPLICATION in
makedefs to point to lua_app and compile it using make veryclean all.

In order to compile Lua applications for Linux use the makefile of this 
directory.

In both cases, compiling for EPOS or Linux, remember to select you Lua 
application setting the constant LUA_APP in the C++ file 
(i.e. lua_app.cc or linux_app.cc) to point for the desired .h file.

